Document: SphereMesh
Path: godot/classes/class_spheremesh.rst
Summary: The SphereMesh class represents a 3D spherical mesh in Godot, used for creating smooth spherical shapes in scenes.

Inherits: Mesh < Resource

Properties:
- radius (float): The radius of the sphere. Default: 1.0
- rings (int): Number of vertical subdivisions. Default: 16
- sectors (int): Number of horizontal subdivisions. Default: 32
- use_triangle_fan (bool): Whether to use triangle fan for rendering. Default: true

Key Rule: SphereMesh generates a smooth spherical surface through radial subdivisions.
